Account Executive
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/29 15:37:37
Ref. JB3045525
Job Description
As an Account Executive you will act as a link between the client and the ad agency. You will play an integral part in the delivery of excellent client service.
The role encompasses:
- ­Setting up meetings with clients and other agency staff
- ­Being responsible for the project management of your clients' campaigns and dealing with the day-to-day work, ensuring it is produced on time and on budget.
- Ensuring through efficient time management that all jobs are carried out within agreed timing schedules to the level expected by both the agency and the client.
- Writing briefs.
- ­Overseeing the status of advertising campaigns
- ­Presenting campaign plans to clients for approval or modification
- ­Handling budgets and managing campaign costs
- ­Writing reports, preparing presentations and keeping records
- Writing Contact Reports, Timing Plans, Agendas etc.
- Should be able to prepare competitive reviews.
- Should have proper presentation skills as well as excellent written and oral communication skills.
Additionally, having a positive attitude is crucial. The problem-solving mindset and the readiness to take on responsibility are major assets that we would be looking for.
Skills
Arabic and English are a must.
Basic knowledge of digital advertising/marketing, including social media.
Project management skills.
Excellent communication skills.
People person.
Positive attitude.
This job is posted in the following Specialties:
Education
Marketing/Advertising
